{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"woozy-pea-kin","description":"## Context\n\nPLACEHOLDER for a brainstorm (do not implement yet). Discovered while claiming the partially-complete epic peak-fir-hilt (72d5): the plan-review claim gate runs the full 4-pass review on an epic as if its plan were FRESH, with no awareness that many of its children are already closed+signed. This misfires for a mid-execution epic:\n- Completion-blindness: the LLM criteria + Pass-4 coach evaluate AC as unmet and may coach you to tighten/ground AC items already DELIVERED by closed children. (Code-grounding criteria grep the tree so they find shipped code, but non-grounded criteria + coach don't reason about child status.)\n- Misdirected scrutiny: a mid-flight epic needs scrutiny on the REMAINING open children, not a re-litigation of the whole decomposition.\n- Latency/cost: reviewing the whole epic+children context is slow (observed a >10min review-plan on this epic).\n\nThis is the design alternative (b) to simply exempting epics from the claim gate (option a). Option (b): make the review COMPLETION-AWARE for container tickets — assemble_context already pulls children; annotate which are closed+signed (done) vs open, so the criteria + coach treat delivered AC as met and scope scrutiny to the open remainder. Possibly adjust routing for containers.\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n- A decision (brainstorm) on (a) exempt epics from the plan-review claim gate vs (b) completion-aware container review vs a hybrid, with rationale.\n- If (b): the review recognizes closed+signed children and does not coach/flag already-delivered AC; scrutiny is scoped to the open remainder.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Brainstorm + decision recorded (a vs b vs hybrid).\n- [ ] If pursued: container (epic/story-with-children) plan-review is completion-aware (delivered AC treated as met; scrutiny scoped to open children).\n- [ ] The slow/whole-context review on a large partially-done epic is addressed (scope to remainder).\n- [ ] Tests cover a partially-complete epic review (delivered AC not re-coached).","id":"66ac-fd03-6d4d-4249","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"epic","title":"Completion-aware plan-review for container tickets (epics/stories with children)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782509464305531001,"uuid":"c6887a84-bc62-4c75-8216-fb0845b59088"}